  "_comment": "Copy to config.json and edit (start.command does this automatically on first run). Env vars (LLM_BACKEND, LLM_BASE_URL, LLM_MODEL, LLM_API_KEY, LLM_TIMEOUT, AGENT_*) override these values.",

  "_model_note": "For MLX, set llm.model to the exact Hugging Face repo id of your local 4-bit build (e.g. an mlx-community Qwen 4bit model). start.command launches mlx_lm.server with this model.",

